title: Visua Analytics and Application (ISSS608)
text:
1 Welcome to my Visual Analytics Learning Journey
Hello there! I am Phuong. Welcome to my ISSS608 Visual Analytics and Application homepage. This course is taught by Prof KAM Tin Seong as part of my Master of IT in Business program at Singapore Management University. In this website, you will find my coursework prepared for this course, encompassing practical application of different techniques to transform and analyze data.
